      <h3>Uncommon Aspects</h3>
      Probably the most important things to be aware of are:
      <ol>
        <li>
          Due to product availability constraints you might not actually get everything you order.
        </li>      
        <li>
          Due to the above, we don't actually charge your payment account when you checkout. We wait to collect payment from your authorization until product actually arrives on your behalf.
        </li>
        <li>
          If you order a variety of products all at the same time, they may get delivered on different days. In that case, feel free to pick each product up the moment it arrives (for maximum freshness) or in one stop once they've all arrived (for maximum convenience). Up to you!
        </li>        
      </ol>

